Number Guessing Game (Java GUI)

A fun **number guessing game** built in Java using Swing.  
The computer generates a random number between 1 and 100, and the player must guess it within limited attempts.  
Choose your **difficulty level** (Easy / Medium / Hard), get hints, and score points based on how fast you guess correctly. 



